<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Verification Code</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }
    .email-container {
      background: #F9FAF9;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 500px;
      width: 100%;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #282828;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    p {
      color: #676967;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .verification-code {
      color: #1ABC9C;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #676967;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <h2><%= name %>님, 안녕하세요!😊</h2>
    <p>RefHub 계정 본인 확인을 위한 메일입니다.<br>
      하단의 번호를 입력하여 인증을 완료해주세요!<br>
      (⚠️인증번호는 10분 후에 만료됩니다.⚠️)</p>
    <p class="verification-code"><%= authCode %></p>
    <footer>📁RefHub</footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
